'''Brenn''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Genesia]]. Brenn is primarily under the control of local crime lord Eelien Kirat, although Soach, a smuggling and black market kingpin, is challenging this rule. Brenn has great logistical value to the Alliance as a busy major port where few questions are asked.

